data.description: Standout home in perfect location has so much to offer. This 2020-built property represents a new standard of modern living, with an owner's suite on the main level, a covered porch, a versatile home office/flex room, and ample closet space to cater to your lifestyle. Entertaining will be a pleasure with the open concept, dining room, bar seating and plenty of cabinet and counter space. Beautiful loft space on second level, large bedrooms. Convenient location has quick access to US1 for easy commute. Extra yard space provides privacy. Don't miss this opportunity to make this extraordinary house your home.
